                                           batch  requests), or the first
                                           six   characters    of    each
                                           filename  in  the request (for
                                           retrieval  requests),  or  the
                                           first  six  characters  of the
                                           structure alias  or  tape  set
                                           name   (for  mount  requests).
                                           This  is  the  name  appearing
                                           under the heading "Name", "Req
                                           Name", or "Job  Name"  in  the
                                           list  of requests shown by the
                                           appropriate        INFORMATION
                                           command (see Related Commands,
