        FORK                         for  selecting  the  process   whose
                                     memory you want to modify

        INFORMATION MEMORY-USAGE     for  displaying  a  list  of  memory
                                     pages, their contents and status

        SET PAGE-ACCESS              for making it possible to  write  to
