              FOO.LOG.1 [OK]
            @ARCHIVE DRCHIVE.TXT
              DRCHIVE.TXT.1 [Requested]
            @INFORMATION ARCHIVE-STATUS DRCHIVE.TXT
              DRCHIVE.TXT.1 Archive requested
