|       SEND                for  sending  a  message  to  another  user's
|                           terminal
|  
|       TERMINAL INHIBIT    for   refusing   all   types   of    terminal
|                           communication including advice, links, system
|                           messages, user messages, and notices  of  new
|                           mail.


